Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 不要回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 邁步出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼淚是閃閃發光的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每一步 都化為甘霖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需要的東西就捨去 這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在無限廣闊的心中蔓延開來喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,於受傷時刻之外　看不見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若現在開始映入雙眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just Try-again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變得強大 抓住機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 無論何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 都要堅信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢想絕對能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有多遙遠 都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight Fight 更能感覺到明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了打倒支配了在遙遠天空上的星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.54,0:01:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們以第七界層為目標展開了冒險旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.63,0:01:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在身處的是有趣熱帶的第六星界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被魔法蜘蛛絲抓到的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在虎王跟瑪達莉斯的幫助下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,解開了詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.47,0:01:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但為此瑪達莉斯失去了性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.09,0:02:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第四十三話\N海火子 哀傷的重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這裏可以知道那家夥的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是熱的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡遙控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在黑龍角修理好之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.83,0:03:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以讓渡他們接近聖地亞索加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.88,0:03:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡還是個小孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因為你大意到現在為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們被他們打敗多少次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬哈路大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.12,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次是由我親自出動,請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我期待你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會要了渡的小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把他的靈魂交給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我期待你,死亡遙控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有守衛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然聖地就在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.43,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但看來不能輕易通過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡遙控!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟把瑪達莉斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要把那家夥打倒的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們封鎖他的魔術…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們三人合力一口氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有那家夥絕對不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.11,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.00,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡遙控!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.92,0:04:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要替瑪達莉斯報仇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,覺悟吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們這些哆嗦我沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.03,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,囉嗦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你由我來打倒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,躲起來也沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老虎、火子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(咒語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.04,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算把火美子怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這家夥的命已在我手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要用點力的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,球粉碎了的話她便沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,用忍法啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用忍法從裏面逃出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們的聲音是傳不進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要她的命的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就用你的靈魂來交換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.61,0:06:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用渡的靈魂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢吞吞的話她便沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要襲擊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.47,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把靈魂給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王、海火子,我要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話,你的靈魂就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去引開他的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁這時候你們去救火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來你已死心了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,放開火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.45,0:07:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那要等取你的靈魂之後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(咒語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,跳進那裏面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.03,0:07:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣你的肉體就會變成灰只剩下靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(咒語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果想逃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那把劍便會插進你的喉嚨裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡是相信我們才去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切都會白費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,你等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會救你的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣打之不盡呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是說這事的時候嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡的性命便要看我們了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王…海火子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡啊,到此為止了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快解開火美子的封印!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(咒語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逃去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王、海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行,被他逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要太小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑撒旦飛彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,覺悟吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊的對手已完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這大牛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳,小鬼…不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王那家夥自己去做餌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逃得還真快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是機會了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍星丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以為我是多壞達的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.69,0:12:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你會這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來是有什麼原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以的話,能否告訴我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.66,0:12:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許我在找的男人會有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼請你告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能找出他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會變得很大件事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在找的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我丈夫為了打倒多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上了第七界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.92,0:12:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是卻被捉了變成了魔界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼,他現在在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和兒子在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兒子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.83,0:12:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,丈夫被封印在兒子手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼會…有這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,某一天,只有那個球回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在裏面的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是變成了魔界的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的兒子知不知道這事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我兒子相信在球內的是他本來善良的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後為了救父親開始了旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我不知道你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但請你制止我的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人復活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個星界山便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.84,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會讓你的兒子做傻事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子他很精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要好好支持著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的力量只有這個程度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼便由我開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(咒語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拯寒死光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超龍雷拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍星丸,快逃呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.49,0:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不行…動不了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了黑撒旦的厲害了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這便是你的末日了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳,什麼家夥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要太得意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊也做你對手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.79,0:14:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要太囂張呀,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡,阻礙者給我消失吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他打算幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,撒旦火炎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王…海火子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還能動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我便送你到黃泉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂,虎王起來呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡很危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.44,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.29,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去,龍星丸會被咬壞的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把龍星丸的冰溶掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣溶掉呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且,再中多一次剛才那招的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.55,0:16:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也有危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是要那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放棄吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真頑強的小鬼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣的招式中多也不會有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.92,0:16:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話你現在便多嘗一次那樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會讓你成功嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惡魔猛虎飛彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王、海火子,謝謝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥的實力不是說笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要怎麼樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分別攻擊不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們三人合力務必對付了他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,幹吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這群小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要一個不留的解決他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王、海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.87,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看招,撒旦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是時候了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變形,飛龍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.44,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛龍光擊拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火子,我怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我終於集齊六顆珠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夏鬼丸變身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.93,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.06,0:19:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸…爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火子的父親大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.59,0:19:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遲了一步嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難…難道那家夥是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.94,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.43,0:20:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是多壞達大人兵眾之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漁火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多壞達大人兵眾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你終於把我的封印解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的兒子海火子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忘記了爸爸了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.98,0:20:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的爸爸已和武一郎老師一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡遙控!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久沒見了,死亡遙控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饒…饒恕我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.61,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是照命令把你封印而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.05,0:21:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打破自己的器皿的蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過…過分…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是豈有此理的家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在開始把聖地亞索加的畫完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.84,0:21:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使得暗黑龍復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暗…暗黑龍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.19,0:22:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在 陰霾的天空裏烏雲漸漸散去 陽光透過雲層照了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.76,0:22:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩個人仰望這天空的哪個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眩目的彩虹 即將出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,注定出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁著光線還沒有消失的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.49,0:23:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,期待著明天的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.64,0:23:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.22,0:23:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熠熠生輝的彩虹彼岸裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.63,0:23:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吹出了兩個人未來的風
